{"tid":2378044,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"國米告知熱刺李城 想租艾歷臣需付全部薪金","createTime":"2021-01-24T06:39:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T13:55:10.000Z","uid":239336,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2e1aab65f70a5a04f2ce3a8056b73c1c3fa3b2f7","tid":2378044,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T06:39:43.000Z","msg":"據知名記者羅馬諾的消息，國際米蘭已經告知李斯特城和熱刺，如果想要租借艾歷臣（Christian Eriksen），就得負擔球員的全額薪資。<br />\n<br />\n  羅馬諾表示：「國際米蘭已經給李斯特城和熱刺說得十分清楚了：想要租借艾歷臣，就必須承擔球員租借期間的全額薪水，否則這筆交易免談。」<br />\n<br />\n  「目前看起來沒有任何機會，而艾歷臣近6個月的稅後工資約為400萬歐元。此外，國米並沒有收到來自曼聯的任何報價。」<br />\n<br />\n  艾歷臣於上季冬窗以2000萬歐元的價格從熱刺加盟國際米蘭，今季，艾歷臣為藍黑軍團出戰14場比賽，沒有入球和助攻。"},{"pid":"b387063134cf3ae892293612d994f9fa2a241d47","tid":2378044,"uid":147367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T06:41:06.000Z","msg":"中國米仲有錢比人工咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"279cd4f78e46c9c39ce9d25852a8fbdf75b61e25","tid":2378044,"uid":158755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b387063134cf3ae892293612d994f9fa2a241d47","tid":2378044,"uid":147367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T06:41:06.000Z","msg":"中國米仲有錢比人工咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T06:44:16.000Z","msg":"點解無"},{"pid":"b268d31d19476a0eb444a94943289406fa1a31bc","tid":2378044,"uid":3194,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:18:08.000Z","msg":"其實佢幾好波, 搞乜咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe28e6f2a03041cab1dcb087dd6358301fba5c1","tid":2378044,"uid":227784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T10:09:48.000Z","msg":"咁唯有留返比國米了😢"},{"pid":"808d922c25be62dc500a8d8e1f0bd7589a82e438","tid":2378044,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b268d31d19476a0eb444a94943289406fa1a31bc","tid":2378044,"uid":3194,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":